title: New Creator: Crisis of Man
body:
Name: Crisis of Man

Info: The secret weapon of modern hard techno, LA-based techno label Crisis of Man was founded to evolve the west coast techno movement. COM is leading the resurgence of underground EBM and industrial, and will provide unique and hard-to-attain visibility of Rally to the techno elite with their lead talent Selective Response. 

Use Cases: 
Launch - COM will distribute gift coins to their producers to give away to fans/fellow artists/collaborators to motivate Rally account creation.
Holding - Private early release streams, AMAs.
Transaction - COM will sell small-batch merch and limited edition vinyl presses exclusively in COM coin. Est. $800+/mo. Additionally, track mastering and production lessons sold in $COM.

Grant Tier: $666

A 'yes' will approve this proposal and a $666 gift coin grant
A 'no' will deny this proposal
author: 0x5ea400d06Afe7aebae54216aDfD7a4bF5f15F993
